title: Tulsi Gabbard on Running for President and The Next MAGA (A Democrat 2020 Slogan Quiz)
description:
Tulsi Gabbard discusses the false alarm in Hawaii that got her to run for president, and meeting with Syria’s Bashar al-Assad. And can “Join the Evolution” become the next “Make America Great Again?” Matt and Katie quiz each other on the Democrats’ 2020 campaign slogans
